        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Ascended Cores",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "id": "p0072.b006",
      "children": [
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Ascending Unique Gear cards is a lot harder, but still doable! To as-cend a Unique Gear card, you need to use one appropriate Ascend-ed Core (a Labyrinthized ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Ascended Core",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " to ascend from Cycle I to Cycle II and so on). Ascended Cores are guaranteed rewards from some of the Battles in the Tree of Knowledge (see p. 74).",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "icon",
          "symbol_id": "sym.art_texture_light_a",
          "alt": "Art_texture_light_a"
        },
        {
          "kind": "icon",
          "symbol_id": "sym.art_texture_light_b",
          "alt": "Art_texture_light_b"
        },
        {
          "kind": "icon",
          "symbol_id": "sym.art_texture_light_b",
          "alt": "Art_texture_light_b"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
